Package: BARBI
Type: Package
Title: A Bayesian Approach to Contamination Removal in Molecular Microbial Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pratheepa Jeganathan
Maintainer: Pratheepa Jeganathan <pjeganat@stanford.edu>
Description: BAyesian Reference analysis in the Background Interference (BARBI) provides a reproducible workflow to remove DNA contamination from shotgun metagenomic sequencing and 16S rRNA gene sequencing data.
